<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">خ ل س:</span> <span class="c2">(خَلَسَ)</span> الشَّيْءَ مِنْ بَابِ ضَرَبَ وَ <span class="c2">(اخْتَلَسَهُ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(تَخَلَّسَهُ)</span> أَيِ اسْتَلَبَهُ وَالِاسْمُ <span class="c2">(الْخُلْسَةُ)</span> بِالضَّمِّ يُقَالُ: الْفُرْصَةُ خُلْسَةٌ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>